{"tid":434515,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《正義聯盟》試映場初步反應正面","createTime":"2017-10-13T10:55:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-26T13:03:02.000Z","uid":91196,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2150ede50095e44b11535f442f74ec1eb3af14bd","tid":434515,"uid":91196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T10:55:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/13/185504_a2d44cee34850da7a73a92179af05bc3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F13%2F185504_a2d44cee34850da7a73a92179af05bc3.jpg&h=8aa4e7a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《正義聯盟》經歷導演薩克薛達離任，由Joss Whedon接手補拍部分場面，兩位導演的視野及拍攝風格各異，中途換人未知對電影帶來的影響是正面還是負面。從試映場初步反應表示，DCEU好大可能繼《神奇女俠》後再下一城，贏取各方好評。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://Batman-News.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FBatman-News.com&d=msnUDYviB40nqSuaWU5zZLr9WXPazFMcT8p8rn878U0%3D&h=200ee6e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Batman-News.com</a>訪問三位有份觀賞試映場的人士，結果他們均表示熱烈讚賞，而其中一位本身並不喜歡《蝙蝠俠對超人》及《自殺特攻》，但讚賞《正義聯盟》。由於《正義聯盟》涉及多位主要角色如水行俠、閃電俠及鋼骨等正式登場，因此該電影的表現對DCEU擴展而言非常重要。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/13/185516_8d14e48938b7a47ceb0fbe9327daf8fb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F13%2F185516_8d14e48938b7a47ceb0fbe9327daf8fb.jpg&h=d66cde44&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"236d71397cc192896c0dfd19a1ac6108194518d4","tid":434515,"uid":21896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T10:59:29.000Z","msg":"超人呢"},{"pid":"bb1e9a63c37394b8add3d1055a4b5a6278b5a01d","tid":434515,"uid":861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T11:00:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>超人呢</blockquote><br />\n放心啦 實會出場"},{"pid":"193d5474d0ff27b99a1270dd874719c65ce69473","tid":434515,"uid":17873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T14:36:44.000Z","msg":"係真就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/n